#etcsl: line-id=B.4

5. [...] še#-er-kan dug₄#-[ga] šim# {ŋiš}erin-na KA X X [...]
#lem: X; šerkan[ornament]; dug[speak]; šim[aromatic substance]; eren[cedar]; X; X; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.5

6. [... ...] šag₄-ke₄ im-du₈-gin₇ su-za šeŋ₃-šeŋ₃ a [...]
#lem: X; X; šag[heart]; imdu[dew]; su[flesh]; šeŋ[rain]; a[water]; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.6

7. KA IM inim sag₉-sag₉-ge-zu-a di-de₃ mu#-[...]
#lem: X; X; inim[word]; sag[good]; di[speak]; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.7

8. X X zid-da X IM X inim sag₉-sag₉-ge-zu-a di#-[de₃ ...]
#lem: X; X; zid[right]; X; X; X; inim[word]; sag[good]; di[speak]; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.8

9. šudu₃! a-ra-zu-bi mu-X-ša₄ NAM X X X X [... ...]
#lem: šud[prayer]; arazu[supplication]; ša[cvve]; X; X; X; X; X; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.9

10. niŋ₂ šu dug₄-ga-ni šim {ŋiš}erin-na-gin₇ bar zu NE a ha-ba-dug₃
#lem: niŋ[thing]; šu[hand]; dug[speak]; šim[aromatic substance]; eren[cedar]; bar[outside]; zu[know]; X; a[water]; dug[good]
#etcsl: line-id=B.10

11. X X X iri he₂-sud dam dumu-bi he₂-sag₉
#lem: X; X; X; iri[city]; sud[distant]; dam[spouse]; dumu[child]; sag[good]
#etcsl: line-id=B.11

12. [... ...] X nam-til₃ ud su₃-ud#-da saŋ-e-eš he₂-en-na-rig₇
#lem: X; X; X; namtil[life]; ud[sun]; sud[distant]; saŋ[head]; rig[donate]
#etcsl: line-id=B.12

13. [...] nam-diŋir-zu saŋ-ta dug₃-ga-am₃
#lem: X; namdiŋir[divinity]; saŋ[head]; dug[good]
#etcsl: line-id=B.13

14. [...] X ud ul-le₂-a X X X he₂-ni-in-X X
#lem: X; X; ud[sun]; ul[distant time]; X; X; X; X; X
